{"tid":438562,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人返工成日做錯野？","createTime":"2017-10-17T04:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T16:55:18.000Z","uid":26507,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f13d86d4e60ceae50bc68a9aed18103393c8cd","tid":438562,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩FG出黎做野<br />\n做啲野日日一樣，但久唔久又錯一次 <br />\n已經好比心機記住，點解咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬雖然無屌我，不過都好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ab3d401d9c1ff6c8484aac072785e5c0a2b2b3","tid":438562,"uid":29093,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"是鳩但啦， 錯一定有， 問題係你上司屌唔屌你"},{"pid":"9cef05d7242a571431f8a150f2bbc9971d930708","tid":438562,"uid":117821,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"你個比心機唔係講 要真係做出黎<br />\n有時返工比老板屌又做錯野 我第一時間就寫係我本細簿仔本細簿仔寫既都係 提醒自已既野 咁樣就會平時做事小心好多"},{"pid":"b082c3bf2eabdd83592e80d5855b119d1641b270","tid":438562,"uid":52571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老味成日要我執手尾 好唔好意思"},{"pid":"2ac5029692754439a9e606738ae60a4432725855","tid":438562,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個比心機唔係講 要真係做出黎<br />\n有時返工比老板屌又做錯野 我第一時間就寫係我本細簿仔本細簿仔寫既都係 提醒自已既野 咁樣就會平時做事小心好多</blockquote><br />\n我都有呢個習慣，寫係張memo紙到<br />\n但到做個陣，啲野一次過黎，又要快就好易唔記得就做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050bf4dd1cf17ebd7436af96941e79e8a66fff77","tid":438562,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老味成日要我執手尾 好唔好意思</blockquote><br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd36a2867135c7dbe5825fb90f36c6f1a88e18d","tid":438562,"uid":85254,"