e<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我又真係唔太用心去做,可能做D野太悶太機械式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39633e5d16582ee2ad12a05b64d0579b5e9abd4","tid":438562,"uid":9566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"因為你唔識check野"},{"pid":"7979f3c2cbfb211aade035b83257b681fe45f6bc","tid":438562,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為公司人少，好多時同事放大假就要做埋平時唔係自己做既野<br />\n上次同事放假，公司有野要拎去印老細就叫左我去<br />\n最後印錯左返黎晒左幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係幾多錢老細又冇鬧，但個下都有諗自己係咪咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2140ec84cbed16d8621c3a91221911bbdc4fcbd2","tid":438562,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為公司人少，好多時同事放大假就要做埋平時唔係自己做既野<br />\n上次同事放假，公司有野要拎去印老細就叫左我去<br />\n最後印錯左返黎晒左幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係幾多錢老細又冇鬧，但個下都有諗自己係咪咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎緊星期五到我大佬放假，無佢教我做野<br />\n有啲緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151028a56e0c345172b3a01b8d62404da48f2e68","tid":438562,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩FG出黎做野<br />\n做啲野日日一樣，但久唔久又錯一次 <br />\n已經好比心機記住，點解咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬雖然無屌我，不過都好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好怕耐，除咗check多幾次冇其他方法</blockquote><br />\n而家唯有做慢啲，確保準確先</blockquote><br />\n酷比仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n98倍</blockquote><br />\n無買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中唔到又改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入場睇住佢贏呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a47a55bbd0f13a444cb31bd7cb36f3633c95b26","tid":438562,"uid":102562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"明明做得好小心 做完都慢慢check 但有時都會出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881b6970cecba30eda0d60e6fd16be2ec8e70ccc","tid":438562,"uid":30751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"間唔中都有d on9錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859729f7710b8e6cc79e3b293a23f3eed87d1332","tid":438562,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為公司人少，好多時同事放大假就要做埋平時唔係自己做既野<br />\n上次同事放假，公司有野要拎去印老細就叫左我去<br />\n最後印錯左返黎晒左幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係幾多錢老細又冇鬧，但個下都有諗自己係咪咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎緊星期五到我大佬放假，無佢教我做野<br />\n有啲緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"